<tt xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling">
   <head>
      <metadata xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata">
         <category>Digital Certificates</category>
         <ttm:title>Verifying a Digital Certificate (Firefox)</ttm:title>
         <ttm:desc>After you have uploaded your Digital Certificate, it may be helpful to verify that it is properly installed within the internet browser, and that your name, company, and email address appear as expected. Doing so will ensure the Certificate is validated when you sign into the eOffer/eMod system. This video follows the Certificate verification process for the Mozilla Firefox web browser.
         </ttm:desc>
      </metadata>
      <styling>
