   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:08.16" end="00:00:10.30" region="speaker">You may need to verify the information on your</p>
         <p begin="00:00:10.30" end="00:00:11.90" region="speaker">digital certificate.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:11.90" end="00:00:14.70" region="speaker">To check your certificate on Firefox, first click</p>
         <p begin="00:00:14.70" end="00:00:18.33" region="speaker">&quot;Tools,&quot; then &quot;Options.&quot;</p>
         <p begin="00:00:18.33" end="00:00:20.70" region="speaker">Open the &quot;Advanced&quot; tab.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:20.70" end="00:00:23.20" region="speaker">Then click the &quot;Encryption&quot; tab.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:23.20" end="00:00:25.53" region="speaker">Click the &quot;View Certificates&quot; button.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:25.53" end="00:00:28.90" region="speaker">Select the cert you would like to verify then click</p>
         <p begin="00:00:28.90" end="00:00:30.23" region="speaker">&quot;View.&quot;</p>
         <p begin="00:00:30.23" end="00:00:32.93" region="speaker">Open the &quot;Details&quot; tab, and then select the &quot;Subject&quot;</p>
         <p begin="00:00:32.93" end="00:00:34.46" region="speaker">field.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:34.46" end="00:00:36.63" region="speaker">Check that your name is correct as you submitted</p>
         <p begin="00:00:36.63" end="00:00:37.63" region="speaker">it.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:37.63" end="00:00:39.26" region="speaker">If anything does not match, you will be unable</p>
         <p begin="00:00:39.26" end="00:00:41.43" region="speaker">to access the system later on.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:41.43" end="00:00:43.63" region="speaker">If there are any problems with the information in</p>
         <p begin="00:00:43.63" end="00:00:46.03" region="speaker">your digital certificate, you must contact your</p>
         <p begin="00:00:46.03" end="00:00:48.16" region="speaker">respective certificate provider - either</p>
         <p begin="00:00:48.16" end="00:00:50.80" region="speaker">IdenTrust or Operational Research Consultants -</p>
         <p begin="00:00:50.80" end="00:00:55.06" region="speaker">before moving forward.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:55.06" end="00:00:57.93" region="speaker">Next scroll down to the &quot;Certificate Subject Alt</p>
         <p begin="00:00:57.93" end="00:00:60.56" region="speaker">Name&quot; field to verify your e-mail address.</p>
    </div>
